summary: A young and beautiful follower that will assist you on your quests.
descriptionHtml:
Sekatra (Se-ka-tra) is a young female nord follower located in The Drunken Huntsman in Whiterun near the entrance. She specializes in Two-Handed Weapons and Light Armor. She doesn't not have the magical powers all the other followers, but she is a beauty, so isn't that what a good follower mod needs anyways?

NOT REQUIRED, BUT RECOMMENDED :3 : (For the visual effects seen in the pictures)
